parameters:
Male Student: Did you hear?! The Monster Fight yesterday, it
seems the Shark Duke won again! A video leaked online.

Male Student: He's so cool, isn't he? Just half a year since
his debut and he's already been recognized as an S-class
monster. After I graduate, I'm gonna join the organization
too, train hard, and become a monster...

???: Ahem... You guys are really into your chat, which is
fine, but you're somewhat in the way. Don't block the path.
Male Student: Ah... President Memimi...! Sorry, ehehe...

Memimi: It's fine to admire the underworld, but those people
are all unfortunate humans who have been rejected by
society. People living in the light shouldn't stick their
necks out unnecessarily... Instead of becoming a monster,
it's better to study hard and join a good company for a
better life, don't you think?

Male Student: Ugh, President Memimi, you're beautiful today
as well... With good grades and personality, and a 100%
approval rating in the school... You're just too perfect!

Male Student: You have no parents, and you earn all your
tuition and living expenses through part-time jobs, right?
That's so admirable... You're like someone from another
dimension...

She is the student council president of Doritoku Academy,
Memimi Samayama. With her exceptional looks, athletic
prowess, excellent grades, and perfect manners, she is a
respected figure by everyone.

Memimi: (Heheh, yesterday's battle was splendid if I do say
so myself... It seems to have become the talk of the town
already! Oh no, I'm going to get even more popular... What a
dilemma...)

It appears that Memimi has a secret face that she cannot
reveal to others...

Memimi: Alright, school's over for today... Time to go to my
"part-time job." Let's head to the convenience store.
